"""
Optimal abelian variety quotients of modular jacobians.

AUTHOR:
    -- William Stein (2007-03)

EXAMPLES:
    sage: A = J0(389)[0]; A
    Modular abelian variety quotient of dimension 1 and level 389
    sage: loads(dumps(A)) == A
    True
"""

###########################################################################
